  "prompt": "Why do the minions in Despicable Me love bananas?",
  "response": "The minions in Despicable Me love bananas because they are depicted as being instinctively drawn to them, which adds to their quirky and humorous characterization. This trait was inspired by the fact that bananas are a popular and amusing food, and their bright yellow color and unique shape make them visually appealing and fun. The creators of the movie, Cinco Paul and Ken Daurio, along with the animation team at Illumination Entertainment, chose bananas as the minions' favorite food to enhance their comedic appeal and to give them a distinctive characteristic that audiences would remember and enjoy.",
